Even if we stop now,

62
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,480
do you think he'll spare us?

63
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:16,800
In gambling,

64
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:18,360
the key is knowing

65
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,880
your opponent's cards.

66
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:23,440
If we can figure out what he's got,

67
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,560
no matter how strong his cards are,

68
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:29,040
we can make him lose.

69
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,160
Tell me more.

70
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:35,320
Listen,

71
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,480
there are

72
