77
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:49,680
and continue with our plan.

78
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:52,280
Once this deal is done,
we'll leave Halan.

79
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,480
The second possibility is that

80
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:55,920
Zheng Bei already has a winning hand.

81
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,480
But our best move

82
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,440
is not to give up,

83
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,680
but to make him believe

84
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,160
we're still playing.

85
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:04,000
In fact, we're almost out.

86
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,040
After this, Zheng Bei will

87
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:47,120
watch you and Mr. Ma closely.

88
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:49,640
Is it too risky to proceed as usual?

89
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,520
Yingzi,

90
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,000
has Mr. Ma ever failed?

91
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,080
He won't this time either.

92
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,080
It's indeed a gamble,

93
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:11,480
but we make

94
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,480
the rule

95
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,720
and choose the time.

96
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,680
You want to change the schedule?

97
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:26,280
We don't know how much
Zheng Bei has uncovered.

98
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:28,600
Mr. Ma suggests

99
