preparing for the worst-case scenario.

100
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:32,960
Let's assume they know

101
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,240
the exact timing

102
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,760
of our next shipment,

103
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:40,720
and the route we'll take.

104
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:43,720
This route crosses
from Halan to Sheng City.

105
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,440
For the police, that means
a joint operation between both cities.

106
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,680
In that case,

107
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,480
we'll move ahead of schedule.

108
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,560
A slow bird should make an early start.

109
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:58,080
The original plan was on 19th October.

110
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:01,200
We'll now move on the 12th.

111
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:05,280
Even if the two police forces
work together,

112
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:07,680
the ones in Sheng City

113
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,680
can't be here a week in advance.

114
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,720
The 12th is the weekend.

115
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:15,800
Even if Halan police suspect anything,

116
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,280
they'll be short-staffed,

117
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,400
and unable to make it.

118
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,320
Also,

119
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,320
the twelfth October

120
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,560
is a day

121
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,920
even heaven is helping us.

122
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,600
How so?

123
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:35,560
That day is Zheng Bei's father's
60th birthday.

124
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:38,800
Zheng Bei's colleagues and superiors

125
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,720
will come to celebrate.

126
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:43,280
When the police let their guard down,

127
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,120
it's time

128
00:08:47,560 --> 00:08:48,560
for us to move.

129
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:53,040
Have Bai Ling contact the towel factory,

130
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,000
and make sure all the towels
for the next shipment

131
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,040
are done before the 12th.

132
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:59,800
Mr. Ma will give the factory

133
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,480
a foreign trade order
for exporting overseas.

134
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:05,480
Even if Zheng Bei investigates
the factory's overnight work,

135
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:08,040
he won't find any issues.

136
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,440
All of this assumes

137
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,440
the worst-case scenario.

138
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,320
We've already checked around

139
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:17,840
the Drug Manufacturing Factory
and Drug Processing Factory.

140
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,160
No unfamiliar faces in sight.

141
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,800
No signs from the Wanhuang either.

142
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,600
So, it's likely

143
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:28,840
that Zheng Bei is still clueless,

144
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:32,040
unable to untangle the threads.

145
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:33,840
If that's the case,

146
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:38,360
the 12th will be foolproof for us.

