158
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:05,640
Guozhu and I

159
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,120
checked Jiang Xiaohai's accounts.

160
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,160
There's no financial link between him

161
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:12,440
and Liang Jiaju or his company.

162
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:13,680
Either Jiang Xiaohai

163
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:15,200
has an account under a fake ID,

164
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,440
or they deal in cash.

165
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,920
Another possibility is

166
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:20,880
they use an overseas account.

167
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,680
With the amount of drugs involved,

168
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,080
the drug money is massive.

169
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,400
Cash transactions

170
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,600
seem unlikely.

171
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:31,560
Liang Jiaju studied abroad

172
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,720
and runs a foreign trade company,

173
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:36,160
so an overseas account
is highly probable.

174
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,480
And it reminds us

175
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,240
that we must capture them alive.

176
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:44,320
We can't let that much drug money

177
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:46,040
go abroad.

178
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:47,560
Got it.

179
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,240
Sheng City is all set.

180
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,240
Pushers are handled.

181
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:54,000
On the day of the action,
everything will go smoothly.

182
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,120
Sheng City officers will assist us

183
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,400
in Halan.

184
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,240
The team following
the towel factory trucks is ready.

185
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,960
Any movement at the factory?

186
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:01,920
No.

187
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,680
I confirmed with the Director today.

188
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:05,520
The shipment is still scheduled
on the morning of the 19th.

189
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,360
Just in case,

190
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:10,080
I checked their electricity usage

191
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,640
with the power company.

192
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,640
Since this week,

193
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,440
their meters have been running

194
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:17,480
