200
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,440
I'm in a bit of a rush.

201
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,800
Officer Zheng,

202
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:41,200
we're good here, no outsiders around.

203
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,240
Go ahead and talk.

204
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:45,840
No big deal.

205
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:47,600
I just wanted to check

206
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:50,080
