207
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:52,320
I noticed you've been working late.

208
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:55,000
Business is tough lately.

209
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,960
We took an urgent order,

210
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:59,400
and they're paying well,

211
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,720
so we accepted.

212
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:03,520
Is something going on?

213
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:05,920
We're working with the police,

214
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:08,680
but no one said we couldn't do business.

215
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,000
Nothing.

216
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,040
We're just asking.

217
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:14,960
So, the Wanhuang order

218
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,680
is still on schedule, right?

219
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:19,240
Yes, we're still working on it.

220
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:20,360
If anything changes,

221
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:22,160
I'll let you know immediately.

222
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,040
Alright now.

223
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,680
Thank you.

224
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,760
See?

225
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,760
You're not bad at lying.

226
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:35,640
Where's my son?

227
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:36,880
And my wife?

228
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:38,800
We'll take good care of them for you.

229
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:42,040
Please, don't hurt my family.

230
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,200
That depends on you.

231
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,680
As long as you cooperate,

232
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,960
they'll be safe.

233
