234
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,480
Everything is ready.

235
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:37,000
Although your plans never fail,

236
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,960
if something unexpected happens,

237
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,160
and you face Zheng Bei,

238
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:44,280
don't hesitate.

239
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:49,240
