260
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:33,440
Thanks.

261
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:34,520
They're still young.

262
00:15:34,520 --> 00:15:35,440
They'll get there.

263
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:37,240
Enjoy your birthday.

264
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:37,960
We'll come back tonight.

265
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,080
See you tonight.

266
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:44,320
Dad,

267
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:46,320
it's your birthday.

268
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:48,040
