272
00:15:51,040 --> 00:15:51,680
Got it.

273
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:52,520
Don't worry.

274
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,040
Okay.

275
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:01,400
Look at you two.

276
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:02,240
No, uncle.

277
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:04,640
How can we let you work today?

278
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:06,400
Alright, I'll check the back.

279
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:07,360
Okay.

