288
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,640
Where is your brother?

289
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:33,480
Inside.

290
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:33,960
Come, Uncle.

291
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:34,800
They're waiting for you.

292
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,480
- Dad, Mom, Bei.
- Bei.

293
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:37,320
They're here.

294
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:37,800
Bei.

295
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:43,440
Anything unusual there?

296
00:16:43,760 --> 00:16:44,560
No.

297
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,960
Just as you expected.

298
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:48,240
All the cops are
at the chicken ribs shop.

299
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:49,880
Wait.

300
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:51,360
Another person just arrived.

301
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:54,680
It's Director Gao from the City Bureau.

302
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,800
Okay. Keep watching.

303
00:17:13,360 --> 00:17:14,160
Let's make our move.

304
00:17:24,840 --> 00:17:26,120
Dad, happy birthday.

305
00:17:26,360 --> 00:17:27,160
- Thank you.
- Happy birthday.

306
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:28,680
Happy birthday, Dad.

307
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:29,680
Thank you.

308
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:31,760
May you live long and prosper.

309
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:33,160
May your business booming.

310
00:17:33,600 --> 00:17:34,360
Great.

311
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:35,160
Thank you.

312
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,760
Let's eat.

313
00:17:38,760 --> 00:17:40,520
Help yourself.

314
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:41,800
Come on, dig in.

315
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:42,520
Try the dishes.

316
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,200
Zheng,

317
00:17:44,600 --> 00:17:46,120
I really envy you.

318
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:47,400
A son and a daughter,

319
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:50,000
what a lively family.

320
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:51,480
You've raised them well.

321
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,080
They're so filial.

322
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:54,400
Unlike my kid

323
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:55,520
who is always out playing.

324
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:57,200
You should be grateful.

325
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:58,680
Once this case is wrapped up,

326
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:02,000
I'm taking my granddaughter
to the South for a vacation.

327
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:04,160
Uncle's been talking
about this trip for ages.

328
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,240
To Sanya.

329
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,440
But still doesn't want to spend money.

330
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,520
It's not about money.

331
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:10,160
Then what are you waiting for?

332
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:10,920
Another few years later,

333
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:13,120
Uncle's granddaughter
will be able to travel on her own.

334
00:18:13,120 --> 00:18:14,000
Exactly.

335
00:18:14,600 --> 00:18:16,600
No way, not so soon.

336
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:18,560
Mark my words,

337
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:20,400
this time will be different.

338
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,800
When we solve this Halan's

339
00:18:21,800 --> 00:18:23,520
major drug case,

340
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:25,600
I'll retire with honor

341
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:26,480
and go on that trip.

342
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:30,120
I owe my parents a vacation, too.

343
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:31,560
We've been so busy, Director Gao.

344
00:18:31,560 --> 00:18:32,840
I couldn't company them.

345
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:34,000
Look at him.

346
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,880
Once the case is solved,

347
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,120
you all come to Huazhou.

348
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,440
I'll treat everyone.

349
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:41,880
That's the serious business.

350
00:18:42,280 --> 00:18:43,000
We'll all go.

351
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:43,680
I've never been there.

352
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:44,680
Let's drop the formalities.

353
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:46,920
Just enjoy his treat.

354
00:18:47,560 --> 00:18:48,840
You're never sheepish, huh?

355
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:50,040
Why would I be?

356
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:51,400
He's not. Why should we be?

357
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:52,920
Look,

358
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:54,320
Xiaoguang is doing more for Nan

359
00:18:54,320 --> 00:18:56,560
than your own son.

360
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:57,720
Isn't that right?

361
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,520
What are you saying?

362
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:03,880
I watched Xiaoguang grow up.

363
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:05,800
He's a good kid.

364
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,040
When will we officially

365
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:11,600
make him a part of our family?

366
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:15,920
What are you talking about?

367
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:17,720
Looks like Zheng wants a son-in-law.

368
00:19:18,120 --> 00:19:19,200
That's good fortune.

369
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:21,400
I agree with great honor.

370
00:19:22,360 --> 00:19:23,560
Let's have a toast.

371
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:24,040
Stop it.

372
00:19:24,040 --> 00:19:25,320
Go get the cake.

373
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:26,560
Right. Your agreement doesn't count.

374
00:19:26,560 --> 00:19:27,880
What matters
is whether my sister agrees.

375
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:29,640
Get the cake, go.

376
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:30,720
Okay.

377
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:32,880
Help me, would you?

378
00:19:33,600 --> 00:19:34,720
Can't carry it on your own?

379
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:36,320
Need a hand?

380
00:19:36,320 --> 00:19:37,280
The cake is heavy.

381
00:19:37,280 --> 00:19:37,920
Is the cake really that heavy?

382
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:40,560
Look at their tied hands.

383
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,040
Eat, everyone.

384
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:42,960
Come on.

385
00:19:51,320 --> 00:19:52,120
Nan,

386
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,880
I have something for you.

387
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,040
What's this?

388
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:03,600
I sang it myself.

389
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:06,360
It's full of songs you like.

390
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:08,040
There are even Cantonese songs.

391
00:20:09,080 --> 00:20:10,320
I'll go play them right away.

392
00:20:10,320 --> 00:20:11,040
No,

393
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:24,160
my Cantonese isn't great.

394
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:26,600
Why don't you

395
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:29,080
listen to it alone,

396
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,720
when you have time.

397
00:20:33,360 --> 00:20:35,120
Have some more.

398
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:44,560
Nan,

399
00:20:46,600 --> 00:20:48,280
after this mission,

400
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:51,080
I have something important to tell you.

401
00:20:53,080 --> 00:20:54,800
Why not say it now?

402
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,920
I want to hear it now.

403
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:02,480
I'd rather wait
until the case is solved.

404
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:04,760
Once I'm a hero,

405
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:06,000
I'll tell you.

406
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:12,680
Xiaoguang,

407
00:21:13,600 --> 00:21:14,480
actually,

408
00:21:15,480 --> 00:21:17,600
it doesn't matter if you become a hero.

409
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:20,960
I like you either way.

410
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:25,400
So, please be careful on this mission.

411
00:21:26,360 --> 00:21:27,480
I'll wait for you to return.

412
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:37,360
We're eagerly waiting for a cake.

413
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:38,520
What are you doing?

414
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,920
Where's the lighter?

415
00:21:41,320 --> 00:21:42,200
Get out of here.

416
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:42,960
Go.

417
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:44,120
Looking for a lighter, huh?

418
00:21:45,120 --> 00:21:46,400
It is so fun

419
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:48,200
to watch our own love drama.

420
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:51,800
- Coming.
- Coming.

421
00:21:54,120 --> 00:21:55,200
Here comes the big peach.

422
00:21:55,360 --> 00:21:56,720
Move aside, and make some room.

423
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:57,560
Move.

424
00:21:57,760 --> 00:21:58,680
Okay.

425
00:21:58,680 --> 00:21:59,520
Good.

426
00:21:59,520 --> 00:22:01,560
Numbers face uncle, right?

427
00:22:05,080 --> 00:22:06,200
Director Gao.

428
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,040
Sorry.

429
00:22:07,040 --> 00:22:07,880
No problem.

430
00:22:10,320 --> 00:22:11,320
She's out.

431
00:22:21,660 --> 00:22:22,900
Scarves.

432
00:22:23,660 --> 00:22:25,420
Miss, take a look at these scarves.

433
00:22:26,340 --> 00:22:28,180
Hello, Miss.

434
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:30,260
Two colors, very beautiful.

435
00:22:38,980 --> 00:22:40,140
Take a look.

436
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,760
These just arrived today.

437
00:22:43,360 --> 00:22:44,600
See which one do you prefer.

438
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:46,600
We have new ones in the back.

439
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:55,600
Madam, they've been tailing me.

440
00:22:55,600 --> 00:22:56,640
I can't shake them off.

441
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,080
You keep shopping.

442
00:22:58,960 --> 00:22:59,760
When it's time,

443
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:01,360
grab a bite, take a bath,

444
00:23:01,360 --> 00:23:02,600
distract them.

445
00:23:03,560 --> 00:23:06,200
I'll handle the delivery.

446
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:09,040
Is my lunch ready?

447
00:23:09,480 --> 00:23:11,000
Almost done.

448
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:11,600
Wait a bit.

449
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:13,120
Once we eat, we'll head out.

450
00:23:46,940 --> 00:23:54,420
[Youth Palace, Jiangtie District, Halan]

451
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:08,720
They're all following Bai Ling.

452
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:11,160
Today's shipment is crucial.

453
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:12,600
I'll go there myself soon.

454
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:14,640
Everything's normal
at the chicken ribs shop.

455
00:24:15,040 --> 00:24:16,000
Just go ahead.

456
00:24:16,800 --> 00:24:18,000
Once the goods are on the road, get out,

457
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,320
and don't be late to pick up Mao.

458
00:24:24,300 --> 00:24:29,340
[Four Seasons Hot Spring Spa]

459
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:05,960
Madam.

460
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:07,400
Come in.

461
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:13,880
Are you getting a full massage

462
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:14,840
or just a foot rub?

463
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:27,680
Another one.

464
00:27:28,760 --> 00:27:29,880
The goods are out.

465
00:27:30,720 --> 00:27:32,400
My sister has also
shaken off the police.

466
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:33,840
Everything's going as planned.

467
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:52,320
You should get ready, too.

468
00:27:54,360 --> 00:27:55,120
We've lived here a long time.

469
00:27:55,120 --> 00:27:56,480
It feels strange

470
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,440
to leave suddenly.

471
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:08,080
It's okay.

472
00:28:09,120 --> 00:28:10,440
People thrive with change.

473
00:28:11,280 --> 00:28:13,200
Time to move to a bigger playground.

474
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:18,160
Go pack up.

475
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,240
Once we move the goods,

476
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:20,360
we'll leave.

477
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:22,960
Aren't you going in?

478
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:24,000
Just having a smoke.

479
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:25,240
Smoking's not good for you.

480
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,520
You should quit sometime.

481
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:28,160
Fine. After this deal, I'll quit.

482
00:28:55,520 --> 00:28:56,320
Hello? Hai?

483
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:59,280
Are Zheng Bei
and the others still inside?

484
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:00,240
Yes.

485
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:01,120
No one came out.

486
00:29:01,360 --> 00:29:02,720
Okay, keep watching.

487
00:29:02,840 --> 00:29:03,640
Alright.

488
00:29:08,280 --> 00:29:09,160
Xiaohai.

489
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:11,320
What's up?

490
00:29:11,320 --> 00:29:12,240
What are you doing?

491
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,040
If you light up in here,

492
00:29:13,040 --> 00:29:14,200
my mom's going to call the police.

493
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:15,760
Didn't you see the sign?

494
00:29:18,600 --> 00:29:20,080
I'll go outside and smoke.

495
00:29:20,780 --> 00:29:22,000
[Smoking prohibited in the shop]

496
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:22,720
Nobody gets a pass.

497
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:24,240
Even Mr. Gao has to smoke outside.

498
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:28,360
Has no one come out for a smoke?

499
00:29:28,560 --> 00:29:29,360
No.

500
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:32,880
Not a single person?

501
00:29:33,280 --> 00:29:34,080
No.

502
00:30:05,280 --> 00:30:06,080
Mrs. Zheng.

503
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,200
You're too kind.

504
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:10,320
Why bother bring all this stuff?

505
00:30:10,320 --> 00:30:11,520
It's Mr. Zheng's birthday.

506
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:12,760
Xiaohai, welcome.

507
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:13,840
Happy birthday, Mr. Zheng.

508
00:30:13,840 --> 00:30:14,640
Thank you.

509
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:15,680
Perfect timing, join us for cake.

510
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:16,480
There's one piece left.

511
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:16,960
Mr. Zheng,

512
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,400
I'm full. I just ate.

513
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:20,960
Who are these?

514
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:23,200
They are our neighbors,

515
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,560
celebrating with us.

516
00:30:25,960 --> 00:30:27,480
Hello, everyone.

517
00:30:29,080 --> 00:30:30,080
Zheng Bei's not here?

518
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,520
He's out.

519
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:33,840
Out?

520
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,480
I told him I was coming,

521
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:38,000
and he didn't mention leaving.

522
00:30:38,560 --> 00:30:39,360
You...

523
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,600
When did he leave?

524
00:30:40,600 --> 00:30:41,760
A while ago.

525
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,200
I'll just use the restroom.

526
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:49,320
You know where it is, right?

527
00:30:49,320 --> 00:30:49,960
Yes, I do.

528
00:30:50,040 --> 00:30:50,920
I'll come back to join you.

529
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,160
Come back for cake later.

530
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:53,320
Let's eat.

531
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:54,240
Come on.

532
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:23,960
Director Gao, after you.

533
00:31:25,560 --> 00:31:26,560
Only you could make me play along

534
00:31:27,280 --> 00:31:29,080
with a show like this.

535
00:31:29,080 --> 00:31:30,560
Let me help you.

536
00:31:31,280 --> 00:31:32,200
Come on.

537
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,160
Be careful.

538
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:22,380
Zheng Bei's not here?

539
00:32:22,380 --> 00:32:23,540
[Ten minutes ago]

540
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:24,380
[Eleven minutes ago]

541
00:32:27,920 --> 00:32:30,100
Once we move the goods, we'll leave.

542
00:32:30,100 --> 00:32:31,220
[An hour and fifteen minutes ago]

543
00:32:31,220 --> 00:32:32,060
[An hour and sixteen minutes ago]

544
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:36,440
Everything's normal
at the chicken ribs shop.

545
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:37,500
Just go ahead.

546
00:32:37,500 --> 00:32:38,660
[Two hours and six minutes ago]

547
00:32:38,660 --> 00:32:39,500
[Two hours and seven minutes ago]

548
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:45,500
Let's make our move.

549
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:46,460
[Three hours and twenty minutes ago]

550
00:32:46,460 --> 00:32:47,300
[Three hours and twenty-one minutes ago]

551
00:32:50,800 --> 00:32:51,840
Just as you expected.

552
00:32:51,840 --> 00:32:53,420
All the cops are
at the chicken ribs shop.

553
00:32:53,420 --> 00:32:54,500
[Three hours and twenty-six minutes ago]

554
00:32:54,500 --> 00:32:55,420
[Three hours
and twenty-seven minutes ago]

555
00:32:55,420 --> 00:32:56,580
[One day ago]

556
00:32:56,580 --> 00:32:57,380
[Four days ago]

557
00:32:57,380 --> 00:32:58,540
[Five days ago]

558
00:32:58,540 --> 00:32:59,700
[Six days ago]

559
00:32:59,700 --> 00:33:00,780
[Seven days ago]

560
00:33:00,780 --> 00:33:01,820
[Eight days ago]

561
00:33:01,820 --> 00:33:03,820
[Nine days ago]

562
00:33:04,400 --> 00:33:05,960
Twelfth October is a day

563
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:07,760
that even heaven is helping us.

564
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:10,160
That day is Zheng Bei's father's
60th birthday.

565
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:15,000
His colleagues and superiors

566
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:17,600
will come to celebrate.

567
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:19,280
If that's the case,

568
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:21,200
the 12th

569
00:33:21,760 --> 00:33:23,280
will be foolproof for us.

570
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:27,160
[Ten days ago]
Would Liang Jiaju take the risk

571
00:33:27,600 --> 00:33:28,800
of knowing he's being watched?

572
00:33:29,480 --> 00:33:32,320
Can we complete the arrest on the 19th?

573
00:33:32,600 --> 00:33:34,760
Based on the towel factory's order,

574
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,680
the shipment is massive.

575
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:39,280
Drug dealers are greedy by nature.

576
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,280
They won't abandon everything

577
00:33:41,280 --> 00:33:42,320
and run.

